headline: Ronovo Surgical Closes Series D Financing
summary: SHANGHAI, September 05, 2025--Ronovo Surgical, a global innovator in next-generation surgical robotics, announced today the successful closing of its Series D financing, led by Johnson & Johnson’s corporate venture capital organization, JJDC, and participation from Lilly Asia Ventures, INCE Capital and Granite Asia, with a total investment of USD 67 million.
